text: Lena Maria Hawkins (born 5 May 1962) is a road cyclist from Canada. She represented her nation at the 1992 Summer Olympics in the women's road race. ==References== ==External links== * profile at sports-reference.com Category:Canadian female cyclists Category:Cyclists at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Olympic cyclists of Canada Category:Living people Category:People from Wroughton Category:1962 births
